<row><entry align=center>Selects all characters from the start of the selection, to the beginning of the line.</entry><entry><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></entry></row>
<row><entry align=center>Selects all characters from the start of the selection, to the end of the line.</entry><entry><keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>End</keycap></keycombo></entry></row>
</tbody></tgroup></table></para></sect1>  
